<div type="translation" source="bib:Gillet2017_01">

<p>Hail! Prosperity! This is the <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> year of king Rājakesarivarman. We the Sabhā of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, for Mahādeva of our village, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Veṇṇāyi <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> in Miceṅkiḷināṭu,51 through <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vacam-um</foreign></supplied> Pāṇṭiyaṉār Varaguṇa Mahā<supplied reason="subaudible">rāja*</supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> and <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>,52 endowed <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vaicca</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">60 <foreign>paḻaṅkācu*</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">for the supply of</supplied> ghee <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ney</foreign></supplied> everyday <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>nicati</foreign></supplied> for a sacred lamp <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tiruviḷakkukku </foreign>for <foreign>tiruviḷakku</foreign></supplied>; in those 60 <foreign>paḻaṅkācu </foreign><supplied reason="explanation"><supplied reason="subaudible"><foreign>i</foreign>*</supplied><foreign>vvaṟupatu paḻaṅkācil-um</foreign></supplied>, having to supply <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>aṭṭuvatāy</foreign></supplied> through <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vacam</foreign></supplied> us the Sabhā <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>,</p><p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> which is lying engraved <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>veṭṭi-kiṭakkum</foreign></supplied> on the stone <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kalmel</foreign></supplied> before <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>muṉ</foreign></supplied></p><p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, the Sabhā gave, having sold <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>viṟṟu</foreign></supplied> a tax-free <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>iṟaiyiliy-āka</foreign></supplied> land <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>nilattai</foreign></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></p></div>

